# Welcome to Viz.ai
At Viz.ai, we harness the power of artificial intelligence (AI) to transform care coordination and improve patient outcomes. Our comprehensive platform features more than 50 FDA-cleared AI algorithms that analyze medical imaging data—including CT scans, EKGs, echocardiograms, and more—delivering real-time insights and automated assessments to accelerate diagnosis, streamline workflows, and support faster treatment decisions.

## Introducing Viz.ai One
The leading AI-powered care coordination solution designed to revolutionize the way patient care is delivered.
[Learn more](#)

## Clinically Validated
Significantly save time and improve patient and economic outcomes with our AI-powered care coordination.
[See the data](#)

## Auto-Detect Suspected Diseases
Accelerate time to diagnosis and treatment. The all-in-one solution autodetects suspected diseases across a wide range of therapeutic areas in seconds.
[View Provider Solutions](#) [View Life Sciences Solutions](#)

## Therapeutic Areas
* Viz Neuro: AI-powered suite of solutions to accelerate the detection and treatment of suspected neurovascular diseases.
[More info](#)
* Viz Cardio: AI-powered suite of solutions developed to meet cardiovascular needs.
[More info](#)
* Viz Vascular: AI-powered suite of solutions designed to transform patient outcomes in vascular medicine.
[Learn more](#)
* Viz Trauma: AI-powered capabilities tailored to meet today’s rigorous trauma center guidelines by streamlining communications and improving patient response.
[Learn more](#)
* Viz Radiology: AI-powered suite of solutions designed to accelerate patient diagnosis and treatment, enabling radiologists to optimize their time for informed decisions and recommendations.
[Learn more](#)
* Viz Life Sciences: In partnership with pharmaceutical and medical device companies, Viz.ai develops new, customized solutions for treatable diseases.
[Learn more](#)

## What Our Customers Are Saying
* "Our partnership with Viz.ai aligns with our commitment to delivering exceptional patient care by utilizing groundbreaking advancements in technology. This software holds immense potential for transforming the way we approach patient care."
* "Viz.ai alerts my team to potential LVOs in our network and allows me to quickly view them on my phone. This is the new standard for stroke care."
* "This algorithm is a powerful new tool for healthcare professionals to more readily identify and capture individuals with AAA, and, importantly, automatically refer those at imminent risk for rupture."

